}} [[Iva Majoli]]\n| 4\u20136, 6\u20130, 6\u20133\n|}\n\n==Grand Slam performance timelines==\n{{performance key|short=yes|active=no}}\n\n===Singles===\n{|class=wikitable style=text-align:center;font-size:100%\n|-\n!width=150|Tournament!!width=40|[[1984 WTA Tour|1984]]!!width=40|[[1985 WTA Tour|1985]]!!width=40|[[1986 WTA Tour|1986]]!!width=40|[[1987 WTA Tour|1987]]!!width=40|[[1988 WTA Tour|1988]]!!width=40|[[1989 WTA Tour|1989]]!!width=40|[[1990 WTA Tour|1990]]!!width=40|[[1991 WTA Tour|1991]]!!width=40|[[1992 WTA Tour|1992]]!!width=40|[[1993 WTA Tour|1993]]!!width=40|[[1994 WTA Tour|1994]]!!width=40|[[1995 WTA Tour|1995]]!!width=40|[[1996 WTA Tour|1996]]!!width=50|SR!!width=50|W\u2013L\n|-\n|colspan=25 align=left|'''Grand Slam Tournaments'''\n|-\n|align=left|[[Australian Open]]\n|A\n|A\n|style=color:#ccc|NH\n|A\n|A\n|bgcolor=yellow|[[1989 Australian Open \u2013 Women's Singles|SF]]\n|bgcolor=afeeee|[[1990 Australian Open \u2013 Women's Singles|3R]]\n|bgcolor=ffebcd|[[1991 Australian Open \u2013 Women's Singles|QF]]\n|bgcolor=yellow|[[1992 Australian Open \u2013 Women's Singles|SF]]\n|bgcolor=yellow|[[1993 Australian Open \u2013 Women's Singles|SF]]\n|bgcolor=yellow|[[1994 Australian Open \u2013 Women's Singles|SF]]\n|bgcolor=afeeee|[[1995 Australian Open \u2013 Women's Singles|1R]]\n|bgcolor=afeeee|[[1996 Australian Open \u2013 Women's Singles|4R]]\n|0 / 8\n|30\u20138\n|-\n|align=left|[[French Open]]\n|A\n|bgcolor=yellow|[[1985 French Open \u2013 Women's Singles|SF]]\n|bgcolor=afeeee|[[1986 French Open \u2013 Women's Singles|4R]]\n|bgcolor=yellow|[[1987 French Open \u2013 Women's Singles|SF]]\n|bgcolor=yellow|[[1988 French Open \u2013 Women's Singles|SF]]\n|bgcolor=afeeee|[[1989 French Open \u2013 Women's Singles|4R]]\n|bgcolor=afeeee|[[1990 French Open \u2013 Women's Singles|4R]]\n|bgcolor=yellow|[[1991 French Open \u2013 Women's Singles|SF]]\n|bgcolor=yellow|[[1992 French Open \u2013 Women's Singles|SF]]\n|bgcolor=ffebcd|[[1993 French Open \u2013 Women's Single